README

reportgen: A Flask application to create REST APIs and generate PDF and XML reports from data

Installations steps (on Linux and OS X systems)

1. Create a virtual env

virtualenv --no-site-packages venv

2. Activate it

. venv/bin/active

3. Install the application

python setup.py install

4. Please make sure node.js is installed and npm is avaiable

5. Install dependencies

npm install

6. Run application

grunt serve

7. For testing

pip install `cat test-requirements.txt`

8. Run test

lettuce

